---
layout: base.njk
title: Constraint Satisfaction Problem Visualizer
icon: fa-puzzle-piece
navigation:
  - name: "Home"
    link: "index.html"
    icon: "fa-home"
permalink: "shidoku.html"
extraScript: "static/js/shidoku.js"
tags: visualization
cardTitle: "Constraint Satisfaction"
cardIcon: fa-puzzle-piece
cardDescription: "Solve Shidoku (4x4 Sudoku) with backtracking, AC-3, MRV, and MAC. Visualize search trees and arc consistency."
cardTags:
  - CSP
  - Backtracking
cardHaystack: "constraint satisfaction csp shidoku sudoku backtracking ac-3 mrv mac arc consistency search trees"
cardOrder: 6
